{"tid":860742,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無人約 約人又比人放飛機 唔敢再約","createTime":"2018-10-13T14:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T15:06:19.000Z","uid":23229,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b49a1331a07693e4352563e967ffc05aa61b10b4","tid":860742,"uid":23229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:36:32.000Z","msg":"見到身邊啲人好多朋友<br />\n我以為係朋友個啲 出去有時唔會次次叫我<br />\n有啲以為我要拍拖唔得閒 但你有無問過我得唔得閒<br />\n有啲直頭唔會問<br />\n到我去約人 結果全部放晒飛機<br />\n到頭來有同我道歉嘅<br />\n但當初約你地個陣 約左3次4次whatsapp錚多句先覆一句 最後都係放飛機 我攰喇<br />\n反正我適合自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無朋友 好可憐<br />\n但身邊嘅朋友 根本無當你係朋友 仲可憐<br />\n其實毒撚一個更開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e998d70ca8159adf11e89447de5fd6f5a82f01","tid":860742,"uid":59569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"有拍拖仲想人問?"},{"pid":"dcb5350525ce1656536daa32004b17697d43f533","tid":860742,"uid":201274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:37:27.000Z","msg":"係咪你平時重色輕友？"},{"pid":"367f379f6512f892ac572a33220044c153ee5a3a","tid":860742,"uid":23229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"02e998d70ca8159adf11e89447de5fd6f5a82f01","tid":860742,"uid":59569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"有拍拖仲想人問?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"友情愛情唔可以並存？自問自己重友情多過愛情"},{"pid":"d5cfd8a878af77e3f636fca1e4c8bfd023e7d6bd","tid":860742,"uid":23229,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dcb5350525ce1656536daa32004b17697d43f533","tid":860742,"uid":201274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14: